oring the amusement park comes alive with SuperPark VR.  \nIt's an ever-growing world of new rides, experiences and games.\nSuperPark VR gives the player a thrill and joy that can be experienced in a real-world amusement park.  Experience riding a rollercoaster and other major rides from your home using VR headsets, playing different arcade games, and feel the adrenal rush throughout your body. \n\nRides:\n1.\tDrop Tower.\n2.\tRoller-coaster.\n3.\tSlingshot.\n4.\tLoop.\n5.\tFerris wheel.\n6.\tTechno Jump.\n7.\tTwin Flip.\n8.\tColumbus.\n9.\tMavric.\n10.\tPendulum.\n11.\tHurricane Ride.\n12.\tBamba Ride.\n13.\tDisko Ride.\n14.\tSpace Trainer.\n\nArcade Games:\n1.\tBasket Ball.\n2.\tPunching Box.\n3.\tDart Game.\n4.\tArchery Game.\n5.\tShooting Game.\n6.\tGo-karting.\nMany more games and rides coming Soon!!!!!!!", "short_description": "SuperPark VR opens a new way to experience the thrill of an amusement park. It's an ever-growing park with new rides, experiences and games every month as free updates."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://mustplay.com/vr-privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Mustplay games private limited", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://mustplay.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "ROLLER_COASTER", "SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "447790420901557"}}]}, "schedu